F. (2009), &ldquo;Periodic-orbit Theory of Universal Level
Correlations in Quantum Chaos,&rdquo; <em>New Journal of Physic</em>s,
11(10): 103025. doi:10.1088/1367-2630/11/10/103025</li>

<li>M&uuml;ller, S., Heusler, S., Braun, P., Haake, F., and Altland,
A. (2005) &ldquo;Periodic-orbit Theory of Universality in Quantum
Chaos,&rdquo; <em>Physical Review E</em>, 72(4): 04620.
doi:10.1103/PhysRevE.72.046207</li>

<li>Nemes, M.C,. Furuya, K., Pellegrino, G.Q., Oliveira, A.C., Reis,
M., and Sanze, L. (2006), &ldquo;Quantum Entanglement and Fixed Point
Hopf Bifurcation,&rdquo; <em>Physics Letters A</em>, 354: 60&ndash;66.
doi:10.1016/j.physleta.2006.01.028</li>

<li>Omn&eacute;s, R. (1994), <em>The Interpretation of Quantum
Mechanics</em>. Princeton, NJ: University of Princeton Press.</li>

<li>Oseledec, V. I. (1969), &ldquo;A Multiplicative Ergodic Theorem.
Lyapunov Characteristic Numbers for Dynamical Systems,&rdquo;
<em>Transactions of the Moscow Mathematical Society</em>, 19:
197&ndash;232.</li>

