Cambridge, MA: Cambridge University Press.
doi:10.1017/CBO9780511803260</li>

<li>Palmer, T. N. (2019), &ldquo;Stochastic Weather and Climate
Models,&rdquo; <em>Nature Reviews Physics</em>, 1: 463&ndash;471.
doi:10.1038/s42254-019-0062-2</li>

<li>Pauli, W. (1993), &ldquo;Allgemeinen Prinzipien der
Wellenmechanik,&rdquo; in H. Geiger and K. Scheel (eds.), <em>Handbuch
der Physik</em>, vol 24. Berlin, DE: Springer-Verlag, pp.
83&ndash;272.</li>

<li>Penrose, R. (1991), <em>The Emperor&rsquo;s New Mind: Concerning
Computers, Minds, and the Laws of Physics</em>. New York, NY: Penguin
Books.</li>

<li>Penrose, R. (1994), <em>Shadows of the Mind</em>, Oxford. Oxford,
UK: Oxford University Press.</li>

<li>Penrose, R. (1997). <em>The Large, the Small and the Human
