Spectra,&rdquo; <em>Journal of Physics B</em>, 6(9): L229&ndash;L232.
doi:10.1088/0022-3700/6/9/002</li>

<li>Pierre, G., Sadovskii, D. A., and Zhilinskii, B. I. (1989),
